"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/13/2262?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Nonsteroidal antiinflammatory drugs (NSAIDs) (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
